TextBody:
Hello Waseem,
 Thanks for your time on our call today. Today we upgraded to NAA 12.0 in your Tyson Domain. AN additional query was added to the Entra ID collection jobs that requires additional permissions.

Microsoft Entra Roles Auditing Configuration

We also fixed an issue with the ADI Summary report. This required us to back up the reports folder and create a new one. This will require report generation or jobs to run gain for the reports to show up in the Published Reporting site.  

I also sent you an invite to schedule a follow up call: https://nwxcorp.my.salesforce-sites.com/cts?Id=de7fPwlXx.nm.eQV4vusplx50XquwHTLfAXtI9Jxo2I-Z&MeetingID=VEof9wWOsbgggggm3Q8LmhQPPZwIaOv6aSf3ykXsGOE-Z
